We recognize that men often prefer action-oriented, practical approaches to therapy. The clinical team at **Riaz Counseling**, led by **Dr. Manahil Riaz**, utilizes gold-standard modalities tailored to your unique mind:

- **Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT):** We work alongside you to identify and dismantle the deeply ingrained "thought traps" (such as all-or-nothing thinking or catastrophizing) that fuel your anxiety, replacing them with balanced, realistic truths.
- **Internal Family Systems (IFS):** We help you explore the different "parts" of your personality—such as the hyper-critical part that demands perfection or the protector part that utilizes anger—helping you lead your life from a place of core calm, confidence, and clarity.
