### Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)

#### **Will going to therapy change who I am or make me less driven?**

Absolutely not. At **Riaz Counseling**, our goal is to help you clear away the cognitive fog of chronic stress and anxiety so you can perform at your absolute best. Therapy doesn't reduce your drive; it gives you the emotional resilience to pursue your goals without burning out.

#### **How do I know if virtual therapy will work as effectively as in-person sessions?**

Extensive clinical research confirms that secure telehealth yields identical clinical outcomes to traditional in-person care for a wide range of concerns, including anxiety, anger management, and relationship issues. It also offers the added benefits of complete privacy and eliminating commute times.

